strong>Far Diagonal</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/6x6-l2c/en/image50.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/6x6-l2c/en/image52.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/6x6-l2c/en/image54.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/6x6-l2c/en/image56.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"3r U' r' U 3R'\"><strong>3r U' r' U 3R'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(U') 3r U r' U' 3R'\"><strong>(U') 3r U r' U' 3R'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(U') 3R U r U' r' U r U' 3r'\"><strong>(U') 3R U r U' r' U r U' 3r'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"3R U' r U r' U' r U 3r'\"><strong>3R U' r U r' U' r U 3r'</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/6x6-l2c/en/image58.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/6x6-l2c/en/image60.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/6x6-l2c/en/image62.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/6x6-l2c/en/image64.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"3r U' r' U 3R' U r U r' U r U2 r'\"><strong>3r U' r' U 3R' U r U r' U r U2 r' </strong></span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"3r U' r' U 3R' U' r U2 r' U' r U' r'\">3r U' r' U 3R' U' r U2 r' U' r U' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(U') 3r U r' U' 3R' U r U2 r' U r U r'\"><strong>(U') 3r U r' U' 3R' U r U2 r'